These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, ritmeester, vegafina, chaman, siglo
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, fanta, tea, 7up
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, security-guard, analyst, paramedic, entrepreneur
House: modern, tower, futuristic, colonial, wooden
 1. the futuristic house is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 2. the wooden house is the siglo-smoker##1
 3. the tower house is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 4. the modern house is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the security-guard is the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is the ritmeester-smoker##1
 7. the accountant is on the left of the colonial house##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
 9. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the modern house##1
11. the security-guard is the modern house##1
12. the analyst is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Cigar         | ritmeester  | dunhill    | chaman | vegafina    | siglo  |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | juice | fanta | tea | 7up  |
| Job           | accountant     | entrepreneur     | paramedic  | security-guard   | analyst    |
| House         | futuristic | colonial    | tower | modern  | wooden |

