.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different games are played: bridge, domino, scrabble, chess, snooker
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: november, august, june, april, december
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, swimming, volleyball, skiing, snowboarding
House: cape-cod, craftsman, gothic-revival, farmhouse, cottage
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 2. the gothic-revival house is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 3. the craftsman house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 9. the farmhouse house is the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
11. the person playing chess is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
12. the person playing scrabble is the person who's birthday is in august##1
13. the person playing snooker is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Game          | scrabble        | snooker | domino     | chess      | bridge  |
| Birthday           | august   | june | december    | april | november |
| Sport   | volleyball | skiing     | snowboarding | baseball    | swimming  |
| House   | farmhouse     | craftsman | cape-cod    | cottage      | gothic-revival    |

