.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different pets are kept: turtle, chinchilla, lizard, goat, guinea-pig
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, march, april, january, june
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid, amaryllis, sunflower, tulip
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, comedy, thriller, time-travel, mystery
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person who growslily is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
 5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
11. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who's birthday is in october##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
13. the owner of the goat is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Pet      | goat          | lizard  | chinchilla       | turtle     | guinea-pig      |
| Birthday         | march | june | january  | april   | october    |
| Flower   | orchid        | tulip | lily | sunflower    | amaryllis   |
| Movie-Genre     | zombie   | thriller | mystery      | comedy | time-travel |

