.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  project-manager, writer, designer, musician, electrician
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, weightlifting, sailing, water-polo, baseball
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, marigold, daisy, balloon-flower, dahlia
5 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, guinea-pig, mouse, cat
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the designer##1
 3. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person who growsrose is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 8. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the project-manager##1
10. the electrician is the person who growsdaisy##1
11. the writer is on the left of the electrician##1
12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Job          | musician        | project-manager       | designer | writer   | electrician  |
| Sport   | baseball | sailing | weightlifting | lacrosse   | water-polo |
| Flower   | balloon-flower         | dahlia     | marigold | rose | daisy     |
