The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, baking, card-games, sudoku, reading
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, havana, bluemaster, bongani, davidoff
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 2. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who likes light-blue##1
 3. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is the chaman-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is in the middle##1
 9. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
10. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
11. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
12. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Game          | go    | poker  | chess | domino    | billiard      |
| Color           | green | light-blue | ivory  | azure | aquamarine |
| Hobby   | card-games           | baking      | reading      | sudoku        | board-games     |
| Cigar         | havana         | bluemaster  | chaman   | bongani       | davidoff  |

