The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, sunflower, orchid, lily, balloon-flower
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, car, jet-ski, bike, bus
There are 5 different nationalities: indian, egyptian, spanish, german, dutch
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, reading, skydiving, dancing, photography
 1. the person driving the car is on the left of the dutch##1
 2. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the indian##1
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the egyptian##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 7. the person driving the car is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 8. the indian is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who growslily##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is the german##1
13. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Flower      | rose      | sunflower       | balloon-flower         | lily  | orchid |
| Transport   | jet-ski  | bike | car | taxi  | bus  |
| Nationality   | german    | egyptian    | indian        | dutch | spanish     |
| Hobby           | reading | skydiving      | writing       | dancing   | photography   |

