.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, aristoff, fonseca, old-henry, siglo
5 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, mah-jongg, whist, canasta
House: craftsman, tower, palace, wooden, ranch-style
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, daisy, rose, sunflower, daffodil
 1. the wooden house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 3. the palace house is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 5. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is the person playing billiard##1
 9. the tower house is in the middle##1
10. the craftsman house is the person playing canasta##1
11. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person playing whist##1
12. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the wooden house##1
13. the old-henry-smoker is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Cigar   | aristoff      | old-henry | fonseca  | siglo    | alhambra |
| Game   | whist     | canasta     | billiard | scrabble      | mah-jongg      |
| House           | palace       | craftsman     | tower     | ranch-style     | wooden   |
| Flower         | azalea | sunflower | daisy  | daffodil | rose   |

