.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, baseball, ice-hockey, cycling, water-polo
The people have 5 different hobbies: sudoku, puzzles, magic-tricks, juneing, photography
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, june, october, april, january
There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, red, turquise, mauve, ivory
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 3. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who likes blue##1
 4. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes red is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 9. the person who likes blue is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
12. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
13. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| Sport      | ice-hockey | water-polo    | baseball   | cycling   | climbing |
| Hobby   | sudoku    | magic-tricks   | photography | juneing | puzzles  |
| Birthday           | june     | april | october   | january | february   |
| Color     | red  | ivory   | blue    | mauve   | turquise |

