.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  security-guard, nurse, software-developer, electrician, freelancer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, mystery, musical, satire, family
5 different games are played: poker, backgammon, domino, chess, monopoly
5 different pets are kept: hedgehog, dog, goldfish, horse, chinchilla
 1. the software-developer is in the middle##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the software-developer is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is the person playing monopoly##1
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the right of the electrician##1
 7. the person watching musical movies is the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the owner of the dog is on the right of the nurse##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the security-guard##1
10. the nurse is on the far left##1
11. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
12. the person watching family movies is in the middle##1
13. the person playing poker is the electrician##1
14. the person playing chess is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Job      | nurse | electrician   | software-developer    | security-guard       | freelancer |
| Movie-Genre   | musical           | mystery   | family   | satire       | adventure  |
| Game   | backgammon       | poker | domino | chess     | monopoly   |
| Pet     | goldfish    | dog   | horse   | hedgehog | chinchilla   |

 